<HEADLINE>
FT  13 APR 93 / World News in Brief: Sikh hijackers given life
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Seven Sikhs were given life terms for hijacking an Indian Airlines Boeing
737 on a domestic flight in 1984.  The hijackers surrendered in Dubai after
failing to gain political asylum in the US.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>INZ  India, Asia.
</CN>
<XX>
