FT  13 APR 93 / Construction Contracts: New superstore scheme in Cirencester
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
BRITANNIA CONSTRUCTION, part of Britannia Group, has won Pounds 14m of new
contracts. The largest contract is a new Tesco superstore at Cirencester.
The contract includes a 60,000 sq ft store, a petrol filling station and
